{"tid":476590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【不法癖好】涉藏兒童色情物品 《浪客劍心》作者認喜歡兒童裸體","createTime":"2017-11-22T06:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T09:44:27.000Z","uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f6266a943ff2df7eefe8acd92b91c7c6ae14f0","tid":476590,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T06:49:43.000Z","msg":"日本人氣漫畫《浪客劍心》的作者和月伸宏（真名：西脇伸宏），涉嫌違反《禁止針對兒童的買春和色情法》，周二被警視廳送檢。西脇承認犯案並直言喜歡兒童裸體。<br />\n<br />\n47歲的西脇伸宏已婚，太太是小説家黑碕薫。案情指西脇在今年10月，於位於東京都辦公室內，藏有多隻拍攝10至15歲女孩裸體的DVD。警方是在調查另一宗兒童色情物品案件時發現西脇涉案，遂派員到他住所及辦公室搜查。西脇承認犯案，他說：「喜歡兒童裸體，買入了DVD及靜止畫像。」西脇又透露，自己偏好「小學高年級生至中學二年級左右的女孩」。<br />\n日本是在近年修改法律，凡為滿足性好奇心而持有兒童色情物品的人，亦成為處罰對象，面臨1年以下監禁或100萬日圓（約6.94萬港元）以下罰款。<br />\n日本《朝日新聞》/《讀賣新聞》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af76d4a5a5cb2ef543589ac33c2482fa1a3d356a","tid":476590,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T06:49:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171121/57485665\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F57485665&d=%2BLDQ0cNhDhlIe2Hwpj%2B39C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ad04ab59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F57485665&h=aaaed78f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171121/57485665</a>"},{"pid":"2efe4daa6157da99ae38cb0d6fc86c2d5b381bb4","tid":476590,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T06:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04074beafe2abd0878ecb4b5dc4717abc9eec8ae","tid":476590,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T07:02:10.000Z","msg":"好多H漫都正太蘿莉"},{